---
title: Cashew Sweet Cream
servings: 4
tags:
  - desserts
source:
  name: Simple Veganista
  url: https://simple-veganista.com/cashew-sweet-crea/
introduction: A (sort of) whipped cream substitute.
---

Soak @raw cashews{1%cup} overnight.

Drain the cashews and blend with @vanilla extract{2%tsp}, @sweetener{1%tbsp} (honey, sugar, or syrup), and @salt{}.

Sweeten and salt to taste.
